Package mygame

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GameOverPanel
    Notifies user that game is over, offering replay and quit options
    GamePanel
    Game Panel is where the main gameplay will take place.
    GotItButtonListener
    A listener that is attached to the 'got it' button inside the info panel.
    HomePanel
    This is the first panel users see, displaying game title and author.
    InfoPanel
    This panel provides the user with a brief how-to for this game.
    MainFrame
    This is the JFrame where all panels will be displayed in.
    MyGame
    MyGame is the main class of this program.
    QuitButtonListener
    A listener that is attached to the 'quit' button in the game over panel.
    ReadyButtonListener
    A listener that is attached to the 'Replay' button inside the game over panel.
    ReplayButtonListener
    A listener that is attached to the 'replay' button inside the game over panel.
    StartButtonListener
    A listener that is attached to the 'start' button inside the home panel.
